Add documentation for KVM_CAP_S390_PROTECTED capability and the
KVM_S390_PV_COMMAND and KVM_S390_PV_COMMAND_VCPU ioctls.

Signed-off-by: Janosch Frank <frankja@linux.ibm.com>
